## Next Steps for the User

To complete the Speed Insights setup:

1. **Enable in Vercel Dashboard**: 
   - Navigate to your Vercel project dashboard
   - Go to Speed Insights section
   - Click the "Enable" button

2. **Deploy to Vercel**:
   - Push your changes to your Git repository
   - Vercel will automatically deploy
   - Or use `vercel deploy` if using Vercel CLI

3. **View Metrics**:
   - After users visit your deployed site, metrics will appear in the Speed Insights dashboard
   - Monitor Core Web Vitals and performance data

